00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,020
By the time we get there,

879
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,660
the fast travelers will have been gone.

880
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:35,860
What now? Can we make it?

881
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:36,940
I've been there before.

882
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:37,980
It's been built recently,

883
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:38,780
pretty big.

884
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:40,020
It's a holiday,

885
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,500
so it's going to be crowded.

886
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:43,700
If everyone comes out at once,

887
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:45,220
it'll be hard to spot her.

888
00:41:45,440 --> 00:41:46,220
Don't panic.

889
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,460
Let's split up.

890
00:41:47,640 --> 00:41:49,060
Xiaoyan, you're off shift.

891
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,580
Take your mentor home,

892
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:52,100
in case Qian went straight there.

893
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,820
Shihuo, Dayu,

894
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:56,020
take the east and west exits.

895
00:41:56,560 --> 00:41:58,300
Bowen, Zhang Yu, and I,

896
00:41:58,320 --> 00:41:58,940
the three of us,

897
00:41:58,960 --> 00:41:59,820
take the terminal plaza.

898
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,740
Look for any signs of her.

899
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:02,420
Go.

900
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:09,100
Mr. Guo,

901
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:11,220
Dayu told my mentor

902
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:13,020
everyone on that bus is already gone.

903
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:15,700
Then Qian could've been gone, too.

904
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:17,860
She's probably got a lot of luggage.

905
00:42:18,080 --> 00:42:20,220
She probably just left. Can't be far.

906
00:42:20,640 --> 00:42:23,220
Check nearby for any possible clues.

907
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,020
Mentor.

908
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,620
Too many people.

909
00:42:37,240 --> 00:42:38,700
Everyone's going everywhere.

910
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:40,380
How do we find her?

911
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,460
Yeah, Mr. Guo.

912
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:43,660
We don't even know which way to look.

913
00:42:44,120 --> 00:42:46,020
Stay calm. Focus.

914
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:47,780
Sizing people up at a glance

915
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:49,500
means picking out each person's details

916
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:52,820
in a messy environment like this,

917
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:55,700
building a picture in your head,

918
00:42:55,720 --> 00:42:57,260
and analyzing before making a judgment.

919
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,440
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

920
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

921
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

922
00:43:52,640 --> 00:43:56,360
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

923
00:43:56,560 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

924
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

925
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

926
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

927
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

928
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:30,640
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

929
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

930
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

931
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

932
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

933
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

934
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:54,000
♪Someone's still waiting♪

935
00:44:54,120 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

936
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

937
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:07,000
♪It's always there♪
